YN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CqZbDXl.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Retired from the Air Force. I decided after so many years of fixing airplanes, I would enjoy designing aircraft and the equipment needed to maintain them. So, I decided to go for it, use my GI bill and get that mechanical engineering degree I've always wanted but procrastinated in achieving while I was still in the service. Today I had my first classes for history and macroeconomics and I'm convinced I'm going to fail. Hopefully it's just first day jitters, starting something new is always going to take you out of your comfort  zone. Had to vent, thanks for listening Imgur.

tl/dr: started college for the first time and terrified I don't have what it takes</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Mgt5JeB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Edit: Wow, I didn't expect so many people to comment already. Thank you for the well wishes. It'll all work out, just gotta feed the hamster so he starts spinning the wheel again!

Edit #2: Wow! I never expected this to reach the front page. Thanks for the support and advice everyone. Nice to know I'm in good company and have people I can reach out to if I need a hand.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ges3LYN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EngineerInTheMaking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4aRhExO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r7BjlwY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4aRhExO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[lifonaut]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The look of derp</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/frsgyOq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NkryeAO.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/frsgyOq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ALittleDistantShiningStar]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Good job everybody! Let’s do it again next year!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fJkSdJz</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7D77mgt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#betty_white #shelter_animal</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fJkSdJz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jkforbes91996]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I have bought several of his products....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Sk448m4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t6s6l9V.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Sk448m4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Ice2Ice2]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cat care…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NQ6Ob2Z</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lSwroK8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><