ion><guid>https://imgur.com/a/SVuoyX2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FromTheBeyond]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Wait what</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/nmId68h</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/okCIcW5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wait what</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/nmId68h</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[nowthatiknow]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I did a thing. 215 to 130 lbs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y217K3R</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/G2BqJFv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So this is me today at 130 lbs! Losing weight is so damn hard but I finally feel good when I look in the mirror. I have sacrificed my body twice being pregnant and it definitely took it's toll on my body and confidence. The heaviest I reached was 215 lbs when I was pregnant with my second child and I absolutely hated what I saw in the mirror.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VhnflAi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2 months ago at 143.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pGWjOTW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is 6 months after my daughter was born. I used the elliptical every day for atleast an hour and watched everything I ate. I was 185 and nothing was working. I was so depressed but stayed optimistic.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AvLnxsv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is me before getting pregnant with my daughter and I was 190(plus) lbs and I may have seemed happy to everyone on the outside but I was struggling internally every day with how my body looked. I  love my children and they are my whole world but pregnancy is bitch on your body. I finally feel like I have myself back and I'm so beyond happy about it. 

To any woman struggling with their body after pregnancy, I feel your pain and frustration. It has been a long bumpy road to get to this point. To anyone struggling with their weight, there is always hope. You can do it!

I eat healthy and exercise as much as I can (hard to do while managing two tiny humans) but the main thing I learned through this all is to allow yourself to have cheat days. Eat a damn donut once in a while or big bowl of ice cream and don't hate yourself for it. But most importantly never give up on yourself. 
We all have one life and it is best to make the most of it. Thank you for letting me share this experience with you all!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y217K3R</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aticklepickle]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Two best friends</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/csRXGnh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3WiGaqE.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If anyone knows if someone posted this already, lemme know.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/csRXGnh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[IntoxicatedKite]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Waaaaarmm</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pMITDSJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6iZ1wuy.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pMITDSJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MrBenDover]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How to make cats and dogs happy at the same time</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ImjtG7S</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M2n1hbk.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ImjtG7S</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[susanaTerror]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Goodest boy saves a young deer from drowning</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kKiGJf3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5FhTwOM.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kKiGJf3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Norwegianwoods]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Not officially verified yet but it seems to be the case</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XyxP4TK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/64FTcJK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></d